scenes.description: Kobo Kanaeru performs an acoustic version of her song 'Natsukoi' while sitting on a beach chair.
Kobo finishes her song, puts the guitar away, and talks to the viewers about her performance and feeling nervous.
It starts to rain. Kobo, identifying as a rain shaman, attempts to control the weather but gets struck by lightning.
Transition scene showing the beach in the rain after Kobo was struck by lightning.
Takanashi Kiara arrives to find Kobo has turned into a baby. They interact as Kobo babbles incoherently.
